{"id":242415,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/07/维权网-北京维权人士倪玉兰夫妇二审将于7月7日开/","date":"2012-07-24T22:46:20Z","modified":"2012-07-24T22:46:20Z","title":"维权网 | 北京维权人士倪玉兰夫妇二审将于7月7日开庭（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-OzUNYLzW--E/UA7L8FrKuTI/AAAAAAAAJp0/kXd1xb26Ph8/s1600/%E5%80%AA%E7%8E%89%E5%85%B0%E5%A4%AB%E5%A6%87.jpg\"> </a></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-OzUNYLzW--E/UA7L8FrKuTI/AAAAAAAAJp0/kXd1xb26Ph8/s1600/%E5%80%AA%E7%8E%89%E5%85%B0%E5%A4%AB%E5%A6%87.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-OzUNYLzW--E/UA7L8FrKuTI/AAAAAAAAJp0/kXd1xb26Ph8/s1600/%E5%80%AA%E7%8E%89%E5%85%B0%E5%A4%AB%E5%A6%87.jpg\" /></a></p>\n<div><span><br /></span><span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员孙雨报道）本网信息员接到倪玉兰女儿董璇的短信告知：刚接到通知，我父母二审</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>点</span><span>在石景山一中院</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>法庭开庭。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>北京维权律师倪玉兰、董继勤夫妇</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span><span>寻衅滋事</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span><span>案，经过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>个月的审理，原定将于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>日</span><span>在北京市第一中级法院开庭宣判，在开庭前夕突然延迟开庭。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>辩护律师程海表示将再次为倪玉兰、董继勤夫妇作无罪辩护。程海律师说关于倪玉兰被指控“诈骗罪”，寻找了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>个月，终于找到判决书中所称的两位当事人，并为当事人做了证据证词和声明，判决中指控倪玉兰“诈骗”的捐款人也亲自向法院陈述了自己是自愿捐款，并称需要时可以出庭作证。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>程海律师认为在这种情况下，判决中指控倪玉兰的两个罪名（寻衅滋事罪和诈骗罪）起码“诈骗罪”是不存在的，那么二审必须公开开庭，程海律师认为形势比较好。诈骗罪十有八九将被撤销。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>对于倪玉兰是否会无罪获释，程海律师认为可能性不大。尤其是在正常的情况下像倪玉兰这样的身体状态看守所是不可能羁押的，但倪玉兰却被羁押了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>个月之久。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>倪玉兰、董继勤夫妇于去年的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日深夜</span><span>被警方从暂住地御鑫苑宾馆带走后，两人分别被以“寻衅滋事罪”刑事拘留。直到一年后的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日</span><span>，人权捍卫者倪玉兰因被构陷的“寻衅滋事罪”及“诈骗罪”被北京市西城区法院判处有期徒刑</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>个月；倪玉兰的丈夫董继勤因“寻衅滋事罪”被判处有期徒刑</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>年。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-763729778774212081?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/cf87fca3ABE5A687.jpg-150x150.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}